g it this way I've never aggroed the banker.<br /><br />8.  You will need to Pact your pet at least once...most likely twice if the guard is dark blue or higher...so throw BoD on guard as well as Splurt.<br /><br />9.  Fearing guards...don't bother.  It usually wears off in 3 seconds.<br /><br />10.  The exception to #9. If your pet is down to 20% health sometimes I'll fear the guard it's fighting and then /pet back off...this buys me a tick or 2 of Pact to heal pet before fear breaks and guard comes running back. This is not recommended if you are near other guards.<br /><br />11.  Adds. I find zoning is much easier if I accidentally pull 2 at once...ST gets resisted ALOT and root breaks as quick as Fear does.<br /><br />12.  Bring weight reducing bags to hold the swords these guys drop...unless you want to run and sell every 20 minutes. I get by with a Rallic pack, Sharlok pack and Herbilist Pack...that usually lasts me an hour. If I get too filled up I find a newbie in the zone and have him sell for me. <br /></span></font></td>
